Martine McCutcheon stunned as she showed off her impressive figure in a monochrome bikini on Instagram on Sunday. The former EastEnders star is currently enjoying a break in Turkey with her family.  The star looked sensational as she wore a stunning two-piece as she sat on a lifeguard tower while posing for a snap.  She also shared a picture of herself alongside her son Rafferty, seven.  On her Instagram she penned: “Making memories and soaking up the sun with my beautiful family.  “@susonabodrum #holiday #familytime #grateful #makingmemories #sunshine #beachlife.”